subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Who was the first Maharaja of Jaipur?
question_hi: जयपुर के पहले महाराजेंद्र कौन थे ?
explanation_en: Sawai Jai Singh II was the first Maharaja of Jaipur. He founded the city of Jaipur and laid the foundation of the Jaipur State in 1803 CE.
